      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.nk3oUdU4wHeRTn76]{Hive Mind}</p>\n<p>You can use your hive link three times per day, and you can have a psychic link with up to three other creatures at one time. In addition, as a standard action, you and one linked creature can share some or all your senses, allowing you to perceive the area around the linked creature and for that creature to perceive the area around you. If you share your senses with the linked creature, it is staggered while you do so. You can share your senses for a number of rounds per day equal to twice your mystic level, requiring a standard action each round you do so. These rounds need not be consecutive. The effect ends when you donâ€™t take the required standard action to maintain it.</p>"
